definitions.definition: Any member of two related groups of North American aboriginal peoples: the Northern Paiute of California , Nevada , and Oregon , and the Southern Paiute of Arizona , southeastern California and Nevada , and Utah .

main_definition: ( anthropology ) Any member of two related groups of North American aboriginal peoples: the Northern Paiute of California , Nevada , and Oregon , and the Southern Paiute of Arizona , southeastern California and Nevada , and Utah .
